# bhcom-ba (Angular 21)

Logistics SPA with **user** (`/`) and **admin** (`/admin`) portals. Prefer existing abstractions over new UI frameworks.

## App structure (`src/app/`)

Only three top-level folders — no `core/`, `features/`, or `layout/`:

| Folder | Role |
|--------|------|
| `shared/` | Auth, i18n, theme, `constants/`, `form/`, `table/`, `confirm/`, `ui/` — used by guest and portal |
| `guest/` | Public routes, guest shell, guest guards, login/register pages |
| `portal/` | Authenticated shell, configs, guards, features |

Paths below are relative to `src/app/` unless prefixed with `src/`.

## Import boundaries

- `shared/**` — import anywhere (guest + portal).
- `guest/**` → imports `shared/**` only (URLs via `shared/constants/app-urls.ts`). Do not import portal configs or features.
- `portal/user/**` ↔ `portal/admin/**` — **no** cross-import of features or routes.
- Feature HTTP: colocate `*.service.ts` in the feature; promote to `portal/{user|admin}/data/` when shared within one portal.

## Commands

- `npm start` — dev server (4200)
- `npm run build` — production build
- `npm test` — run existing Vitest suite only when asked; see **Testing** below

## Testing (agents)

- **Never add unit tests** — no new `*.spec.ts` files, Vitest cases, test helpers, or test-only dependencies.
- Do not scaffold, suggest, or include unit tests as part of feature work, refactors, or bug fixes unless the user explicitly requests tests.
- Do not extend or rewrite existing unit tests unless the user explicitly asks.
- Prefer manual verification (`npm start`, `npm run build`) over adding coverage.

## Source map (read files when implementing, don’t guess)

- Root routes: `app.routes.ts` — guest routes + lazy portal trees with `portalMatchGuard`
- Guest routes: `guest/guest.routes.ts`
- Portal routes: `portal/user/user.routes.ts`, `portal/admin/admin.routes.ts`
- App URLs + portal kind: `shared/constants/app-urls.ts` (barrel), `guest-urls.ts`, `user-urls.ts`, `admin-urls.ts`, `portal-kind.type.ts` — **never hardcode route paths**; see `.cursor/rules/app-urls.mdc`
- Shared data: `shared/constants/bih-cities.ts` (`BIH_CITY_OPTIONS`); `shared/constants/user-entity-status.ts` (`UserEntityStatus` — interim); portal icons: `portal/admin/admin-page-icons.ts`, `portal/user/user-page-icons.ts` — see `shared-constants.mdc`, `entity-status.mdc`
- Shared utils: `shared/utils/date-input.ts`, `shared/utils/normalize-for-search.ts` — see `shared-utils.mdc`
- Auth: `shared/core/auth/` — session types (`AuthUser`, `Session` in `auth.model.ts`); stub login until API; company registration stub in `guest/pages/register/register-company.service.ts`
- Guards: `guest/guards/guest.guard.ts` (`guestGuard`); `portal/guards/portal-match.guard.ts`
- Portal config: `portal/common/models/portal-config.model.ts`, `portal/user/user-portal.config.ts`, `portal/admin/admin-portal.config.ts`
- Portal shell: `portal/shell/` — `PortalShellComponent`, `PortalSidebarComponent`, `PortalTopbarComponent`, `shared.sidebar.service.ts`
- Sidebar nav: `portal/user/user-nav.config.ts`, `portal/admin/admin-nav.config.ts` (types in `portal/common/models/nav.model.ts`)
- Theme/i18n: `shared/core/theme/`, `shared/core/i18n/`
- Forms: `shared/form/` (barrel `index.ts`); Tables: `shared/table/` (barrel `index.ts`); Confirm: `shared/confirm/` (`ConfirmService`, global `ConfirmDialogComponent` in `app.html`)
- Features: `portal/user/features/` (dashboard, routes, cargo, storage); `portal/admin/features/` (dashboard, settings, users, vehicles, warehouses)
- i18n: `public/assets/en.json` + `bh.json`
- Theme/breakpoints: `src/styles.scss`, `src/styles/_breakpoints.scss`, `portal/shell/viewport.ts`
- Shared UI widgets: `shared/ui/` — brand-mark, language-picker, theme-picker, metric-card, quick-action-card, page-title, page-header, primary-action-link, **route-display**, **vehicle-display**, **status-badge**

## Auth routing (guards)

| Guard | Where | Behavior |
|-------|-------|----------|
| `guestGuard` | `/`, `/sign-in`, `/login`, `/register`, `/admin/login` | Unauthenticated → allow; authenticated → session portal home |
| `portalMatchGuard` | `''` and `admin` lazy trees | Unauthenticated → `/`; wrong portal → correct portal home |

## Layout behavior (do not reimplement ad hoc)

- **Desktop:** persistent sidebar (`SidebarService.collapsed`), panel collapse/expand in brand row.
- **Mobile (≤768px):** topbar hamburger → drawer; brand shows portal suffix + close (X).
- **Main scroll:** `.portal-shell__content` (portal) or guest shell outlet area (guest).

## References for patterns

- **Portal CRUD (canonical):** `portal/admin/features/vehicles/` — `data/`, `form/`, `table/` layout; see `portal-feature.mdc`
- **User CRUD:** `portal/user/features/routes/` — same `data/` / `form/` / `table/` layout
- Stepper create-only: `guest/pages/register/`
- Stepper create + edit: `portal/admin/features/vehicles/form/` — `[stepperMode]` + `[stepperDataReady]`
- Stepper framework: `shared/form/form-page/`, `shared/form/form-stepper/`, `form.utils.ts` (`ValidationState`, free navigation, mobile chip rail) — see `forms.mdc`
- Table page (service loader + delete): `portal/admin/features/vehicles/table/` — see `portal-feature.mdc`, `confirm.mdc`
- Guest login: `guest/pages/login/user-login-page.*`, `admin-login-page.*`
- Guest register: `guest/pages/register/register-company-page.*` (+ `register-company.service.ts` stub)
- Dashboard KPI card: `shared/ui/metric-card/` — `MetricCardComponent` for title + value + subtitle stats; parent wraps in `routerLink` when tile should navigate
- Dashboard action tile: `shared/ui/quick-action-card/` — `QuickActionCardComponent` for portal quick-action grids (monochrome icon, `routerLink`)
- Admin dashboard (reference): `portal/admin/features/dashboard/` — `admin-dashboard-page.*`, `admin-dashboard.actions.config.ts`, `data/admin-dashboard.service.ts`; admin nav has Dashboard section (`ADMIN_HOME_URL`, `LucideLayoutGrid`)
- **Portal page title:** `PageTitleComponent` — `titleKey` + `subtitleKey` + `pageIcon` (`AdminPageIcons` / `UserPageIcons`); see `page-title.mdc`
- **Route display cell:** `RouteDisplayComponent` (`shared/ui/route-display/`) — origin → destination in route/cargo tables; see `tables.mdc`
- **Vehicle display cell:** `VehicleDisplayComponent` (`shared/ui/vehicle-display/`) — vehicle name + plate in user routes table; see `tables.mdc`
- **Status badge cell:** `StatusBadgeComponent` (`shared/ui/status-badge/`) — entity `status` pill in user route/cargo/storage tables; all entities will get status over time — see `entity-status.mdc`, `tables.mdc`
- **BiH city autocomplete:** `BIH_CITY_OPTIONS` + `type: 'autocomplete'` — see `shared-constants.mdc`, `forms.mdc`
- **Table page create CTA:** list pages with a create route use `PageHeaderComponent` + `PageTitleComponent` + `PrimaryActionLinkComponent` — page owns `createUrl` / `createLabelKey`; see `page-title.mdc`, `portal-feature.mdc`
